    <ProjectHeader bsColumn="col-6 col-sm-3" bgColor="bg-black" imagePath="../Images/henry-js/henrys-hot-sauce.png" imageAlt="Henry J's Hot Sauce"/>
    <div class="row justify-content-center w-100 bg-body">
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-6 my-5 pt-5">
            <p class="text-body my-3">
                Henry J’s Taco House is a beloved Mexican restaurant located in Des Moines, Iowa, that has been serving up 
                delicious dishes since 1973. Their menu features a variety of classic Mexican favorites, including flavorful 
                flour tacos, hearty enchiladas, and satisfying taco salads. Henry J’s Taco House is the perfect spot for a 
                delicious meal.
            </p>
            <p class="fw-semibold text-body mb-1">The Problem</p>
            <p class="text-body">
                Currently the hot sauce is poured into styrofoam cups with plastic lids. The styrofoam and plastic are 
                easy to break, don’t look aesthetically pleasing, and make a mess when you try to pour the hot sauce out.  
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center w-100">
            <div class="col-10 col-sm-4 col-md-3 col-lg-2 mt-3 mt-sm-0">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="../Images/henry-js/henrys-styrofoam1.jpg" alt="Hot sauce in styrofoam"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-10 col-sm-4 col-md-3 col-lg-2 mt-3 mt-sm-0">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="../Images/henry-js/henrys-styrofoam2.jpg" alt="Hot sauce in styrofoam lid closed"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-6 my-5">
            <p class="fw-semibold text-body mb-1">The Solution</p>
            <p class="text-body">
                I began my design process with rough sketches, then moved on to creating digital designs in Illustrator.
                From there, I selected two different glass bottles to serve as the hot sauce packaging, offering both
                practicality and visual appeal.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="my-3 row justify-content-center w-100 align-items-stretch">
            <div class="col-sm-10 col-lg-7">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="../Images/henry-js/Henrys-design-black.png" alt="black hot sauce label"/>
            </div>
            <div class="col-8 col-sm-4 col-lg-2 d-flex mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="../Images/henry-js/Henrys-bottle-black.jpg" alt="hot sauce bottle with black label"/>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="my-3 row justify-content-center w-100 align-items-stretch">
            <div class="col-8 col-sm-4 col-lg-2 d-flex order-1 order-lg-0 mt-3 mt-lg-0">
