    <ProjectHeader bsColumn="col-2 pixel-img" bgColor="bg-weiner" imagePath="../Images/weiner-run/weiner-fire.png"  imageAlt="Weiner on fire running on a grill"/> 
    <div class="row justify-content-center w-100">
        <div class="col-10 col-md-7 col-lg-6 my-5 pt-5">
            <p class="text-body">
                Weiner Run is a pixel art endless runner mobile game created with Unity and C#.  In Weiner Run, players 
                take on the role of a Weiner trying to jump from grill to grill and avoid getting sliced. Along the way,
                they collect power-ups like ketchup, mustard, and pickles, and unlock fun costumes to dress up their 
                Weiner in. The game also features a global “weinerboard” leaderboard, where players can compete against 
                each other for the top spot.
            </p>
            <p class="text-body">
                As the sole developer behind Weiner Run, I was responsible for all aspects of the game’s design and 
                development. This includes programming the game mechanics, designing the levels and obstacles, creating the 
                pixel art graphics and animations, and implementing the global leaderboard feature.
            </p>
        </div>
